# UserController

# GET get

GET /users/{id}

# 请求参数

名称位置类型必选说明
idpathstring是none
Authorizationheaderstring否none

返回示例

成功

{
  "flag": false,
  "code": 0,
  "message": "",
  "data": {
    "id": "",
    "username": "",
    "nickname": "",
    "gender": "",
    "enabled": 0,
    "lastLoginIp": "",
    "lastLoginTime": "",
    "roles": [
      {
        "name": "",
        "title": "",
        "id": "",
        "createdTime": "",
        "updatedTime": ""
      }
    ]
  }
}

# 返回结果

状态码状态码含义说明数据模型
200OKopen in new window成功Inline
